{
  "stem": "3012.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I immediately called my parents and, through certain masking metaphors, I let them know what's going on and that I am arriving in the afternoon.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I left, of course, everything I had at my-- at our friend's place.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I only took my purse and the book.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Got on the train way, and proceeded to the railway station.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And somebody whom I found rather suspicious wanted to strike up a conversation.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And by that time, I was suspecting the Gestapo and the SS and-- and-- and all-- all these evil people around us that they want to do me in.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I jumped off, I took a cab, and rode to the station.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I did not have any ID but one piece of paper that telled the world-- told the world that I am an Israelite, which is not the best ID in time of a Nazi invasion, of course.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was an official Hungarian document?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, with the religion.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, sure.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And if you were Christian, Roman Catholic.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "God forbid not to declare religion.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was Hungary.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I figured that, if I-- if I walk into a compartment where there are officers-- Hungarian officers, military officers-- probably I could get away with it.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't particularly look 'Jewish,' quote, unquote.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And with no luggage but a book and a small purse, I was hoping for the best.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I just called and left a message that I'm going home on vacation.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nothing else.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm sure they knew it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, they-- they knew what was all about.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it-- it-- it was a trying journey because I was afraid any minute that somebody would come in and-- and would ask questions.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Nobody bothered me.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
